1.0.name: wordpress/dreamobjects
1.0.description:
DreamHost has its own Cloud - DreamObjects™ - an inexpensive, scalable object storage service that was developed from the ground up to provide a reliable, flexible cloud storage solution for entrepreneurs and developers. It provides a perfect, scalable storage solution for your WordPress site.

Well now that we've gotten the sales-pitch out of the way, DreamObjects Connections will plugin your WordPress site into DreamObjects, tapping into the amazing power of automated backups, fileuploaders, and more!

Please do not open DreamHost Support Tickets for this plugin. Honestly, the support techs are fantastic, but they can't debug this yet, so they'll just send you here anyway. Post in the support forum here, and I'll get to you ASAP.

Backup Features

  • Automatically backs up your site (DB and files) to your DreamObjects
